regular-body:
I have so many things to do I don’t understand why I’m actually scared to do them?? WTF why am i such lazy shit?? AP English i still need to pick my books, gym requirement needs to get filled, I need to learn how to fucking drive

why am i considering it an accomplishment that I woke up at 7:30 and took a shower and havent gone back to sleep yet????????? im gonna say that to mom and she probably had a bad day today b/c people are shitty and  shes gonna tell me exactly what im thinking rn in that i need to get off my ass and get cracking or else im totally fucked since summer’s, like. half over, and i havent done a goddamn thing

i cant even do the things i like? like, i’m forgetting how to draw or rp because my rping is shitty and probably problematic i got called on it once and even though their complaint wasnt a valid one it still has me thinking, maybe im just Not Actually That Good a Person???? and i dont really like it anymore i loke sleeping im good at sleeping i cann do that for a while

am i actually depressed or do i have it so far implanted in my mind that for the past year+, i have been, so i’ve managed to make myself depressed? is it even real, or am i just trivializing the things other people go through because i feel like theres some ulterior gain like attention or something but there ISNT, if anything it’s driving me away from everyone? im not even sure where to start on liking things again? like, i’m stuck being up-to-date with the things i like circa 2012, sans probably cartoons and homestuck (++ i like parts of homestuck nobody else thinks about the most and it’s  like my Default Interest despite having 0 canon and me not writing  anything because I Fear Productivity, apparently. as in chest gets kinda tight thinking about doing work why am i so lazy i DO WORK ON THINGS TO TRY AND CHILL B/C IM FREAKING OUT ABOUT THINKING ABOUT DOING THINGS HELP) 

i want to find new music but i dont know where to look, if ill like it, if ill remember what it is and ever come back to it

i like lots of music but its always “no, the moment isnt right, i cant listen to this” and then i end up not listening to anything and wishing i were asleep instead

which is what imm doing now, if i didnt have my lil sis  to make sure doesnt burn the house down and also cook her tortellini
